00:41:56.227 --> 00:41:56.471
You must remain filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit.

00:41:56.471 --> 00:42:01.406
What is the Father saying to you?

00:42:01.406 --> 00:42:06.874
Are you a bandwagon Christian following trends?

00:42:06.874 --> 00:42:13.560
Do not follow trends; follow the voice of the Lord.

00:42:13.560 --> 00:42:20.497
Don't follow my channel and say, 'Brother Brandon said this, so it must be good.

00:42:20.497 --> 00:42:24.539
' I'm human; I can miss it.

00:42:27.904 --> 00:42:29.966
You must be led by the Spirit for yourself.

00:42:29.966 --> 00:42:34.960
I'm nobody special, just a sinner saved by grace.

00:42:43.090 --> 00:42:43.300
But I'm hungry and thirsty.

00:42:43.300 --> 00:42:45.405
Let's pray together.

00:42:57.310 --> 00:42:57.605
You say, 'Brandon, I'm not going to be that 1% that loses everything.

00:42:57.605 --> 00:43:02.017
' Father, we thank you for every person here.

00:43:08.578 --> 00:43:08.720
We believe they are going to be that 1% who die to self.

00:43:15.880 --> 00:43:16.200
You must die to self.

00:43:16.200 --> 00:43:23.080
A dead man doesn't have emotions, doesn't feel rejection or anger.

00:43:31.453 --> 00:43:31.622
A dead man is dead.

00:43:33.320 --> 00:43:38.244
I want to be less of me and more of Him.

00:43:43.490 --> 00:43:45.338
A dead man doesn't get upset when people persecute him.

00:43:45.338 --> 00:43:48.240
1%—that number is not very big.

00:43:48.240 --> 00:43:53.839
Oh, that you would be so close to Him.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
All it takes is one second for your life to never be the same.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
It's just a yielded surrender.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Father, I thank you for your presence.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
We ask for revival even on this street.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
I pray for Megan; I thank you that she is healed of that cough right now.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
I pray for everyone here today, that you're healed and whole in the name of Jesus from every virus and plague.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
I call you healed and whole.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.050
I thank you, Father, that they're filled with the Holy Ghost and that there's an anointing on them to set the captives free.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
I thank you that you will provide everything they need.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
I pray marriages be restored and children come home.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
I call wayward children home right now.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
I call for the blinders to come off their eyes.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
Faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Now they're healed, now they're delivered.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
We believe and receive today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
Harvesters and sowers will go hand in hand.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Amen.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
If this video blessed you, please subscribe.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
We'll never ask you for money.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
If anybody asks you for anything on social media, it is not us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
We won't ask for crypto or donations.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Freely we give.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
God is a rewarder of those that seek Him.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
The Lord said, 'Brandon, I want you to pray over that picture and bless that family.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
' Someone sent a picture of their family.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
If you want us to pray for your family, send a picture.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put their name on the back so I know who it is.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
My wife, children, and I will pray over those pictures every day.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
It's an honor.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
God bless you all.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Have a wonderful day.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
